title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update -  Sim Update VIII - What to expect
description:
Beta testing of Sim Update 8 has started and as part of this Asobo has released a list of fixes which are included in the latest Sim Update which is planned to be released in early March. In this video we will look at the fixes included and also have a look at how you can participate in testing.
